item.title: Three Management Leadership Traps You Need to Avoid with Barbara Mitchell
item.description:
LEADERSHIP TRAPS

CONGRATULATIONS – you’re a manager now.

If you secretly feel like the cat who finally caught the mouse and are not quite sure how to avoid common management leadership traps, you’re not alone. Today’s guest, HR pro Barbara Mitchell has years of experience helping new and seasoned managers side-step leadership traps and can help you maximize your impact and influence as well as build trust and and high performance teams...
